'''埃爾拉多黃金'''（'''Eldorado Gold'''）是一家位於[[加拿大|加拿大]][[溫哥華|溫哥華]]的[[金礦開採|金礦開採]]公司，在數個海外國家有金礦開採業務。<ref name="#1"/>

==收購==
2009年8月宣佈將以20億加元的價格收購[[澳華黃金|澳華黃金]]。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.reuters.com/article/asiaDealsNews/idUSTRE57P3LR20090826 | work=Reuters | title=Eldorado to buy Sino Gold for $2 billion | date=2009-08-26 | accessdate=2013-11-25 | archive-date=2009-08-30 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090830101213/http://www.reuters.com/article/asiaDealsNews/idUSTRE57P3LR20090826 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

2011年12月宣佈將以25億加元的價格收購[[歐洲金田|歐洲金田]]，這是該公司最大的收購項目。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-18/eldorado-to-buy-european-goldfields-for-2-41-billion-to-expand-in-europe.html |title=Eldorado Falls the Most in Two Years Amid Plan to Buy European Goldfields |date=December 20, 2011 |accessdate=2013-11-25 |archive-date=2013-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131202231849/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-18/eldorado-to-buy-european-goldfields-for-2-41-billion-to-expand-in-europe.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

